name: Tote Bag ~ Bunny & The Moon
description:
Featuring Bunny & The Moon, these 100% unbleached 4oz cotton tote bags are woven at Fair Trade Factories in India.

The front of the bag is printed with Bunny & The Moon illustration by Zosienka. The back of the bag is plain.

Can be machine washed at 40 degrees.

Dimensions: bag measures 42H x 37W cm.

Tote Bags are folded and delivered in a bubble envelope.

name: Tea Towel ~ The Walrus and the Ship
description:
The walrus swimming silently in the shadow of the ship.

These tea towels are woven at Fair Trade Factories in India and printed with eco-friendly ISO 14001 quality inks in the UK.

A natural shade, this 100% unbleached 4oz cotton tea towel is screen printed with a single colour illustration. 
Can be machine washed at 40 degrees.

As the tea towels are carefully produced by hand, natural variances may be expected.

Dimensions: tea towel measures 50cm x 70cm.

Design by Zosienka

name: A6 Plain Notebooks
description:
Ten plain page notebooks with illustrated covers.

All you'd hope for in a notebook; a beautiful place to store thoughts, sketches and crazy, profound ideas. The covers feature animals and patterns on a colour palatte of peach, berry, sage and snow.

The covers are printed digitally on a thick protective card and all the paper in the notebook is 100% recycled.

Dimensions: 
A6 (148mm x 105mm)
36 plain white pages

Notebooks will be delivered in a hard back envelope.
